## Build Setup

### Installation
```bash
npm install
```

### Development Build
```bash
npm run dev  # Watch mode for development
```

### Production Build
```bash
npm run build:all  # Build everything (ESM, CJS, bundled)
```

### Output Structure
```
dist/
├── esm/           # ES Module output
├── cjs/           # CommonJS output
├── types/         # TypeScript declarations
├── bundles/       # Optimized bundles (.esm.js, .umd.js)
└── browser/       # Standalone browser bundle
```

### Usage Examples

**ES Modules (Modern Browsers/Node):**
```javascript
import { AttestationService, SolanaProvider } from 'solana-kyc-compliance-sdk';
```

**CommonJS (Node.js):**
```javascript
const { AttestationService } = require('solana-kyc-compliance-sdk');
```

**Browser (Script Tag):**
```html
<script src="https://unpkg.com/solana-kyc-compliance-sdk/dist/browser/solana-kyc-compliance.min.js"></script>
<script>
  const { SolanaKYC } = window;
</script>
```

**Submodule Import (Tree-shaking):**
```javascript
import { checkTokenCompliance } from 'solana-kyc-compliance-sdk/core-api';
```